{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-bang-space-after/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/custom-property-empty-line-before/","description":"property-case Specify lowercase or uppercase for properties. The --fix option on the command line can automatically fix all of the problems…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"property-case\"><a href=\"#property-case\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>property-case</h1>\n<p>Specify lowercase or uppercase for properties.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**     ↑\n * These properties */</span></code></pre>\n<p>The <code>--fix</code> option on the <a href=\"../../../../user-guide/cli/#autofixing-errors\">command line</a> can automatically fix all of the problems reported by this rule.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#options\">Options</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#lower\">\"lower\"</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#upper\">\"upper\"</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"lower\"|\"upper\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"lower\"><a href=\"#lower\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"lower\"</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">WIDTH</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">widtH</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-Radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">5px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">-WEBKIT-animation-duration</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3s</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (orientation: landscape) {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">WiDtH</span>: 500<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">5px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">-webkit-animation-duration</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3s</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (orientation: landscape) {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">width</span>: 500<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"upper\"><a href=\"#upper\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"upper\"</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">widtH</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-Radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">5px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">-WEBKIT-animation-duration</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3s</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (orientation: landscape) {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">WiDtH</span>: 500<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">WIDTH</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">BORDER-RADIUS</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">5px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">-WEBKIT-ANIMATION-DURATION</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3s</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (orientation: landscape) {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">WIDTH</span>: 500<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/property-case.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/property-case/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/property-case/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/property-case/index.html.74e614a42267280c9d19421d84596010.json"}